about: Dr. Shweta Raje is a Gynecologist and Gynecological Endoscopic Surgeon at Womens Hospital, Khar (West), Mumbai, which is a premiere laparoscopic institute and 3D laparoscopy center. After completing MD (OBGYN)and DNB (OBGYN) she did fellowship in Gynecological Endoscopy. She scored 1 st rank in University in her MD (OBGYN) examination. She has 14 years of experience in the field of Gynaecological Endoscopy. She has many research publications in International journals to her credit and has delivered lectures and presented research papers in national and international conferences. Dr. Shweta Raje is a national faculty at CeMAST and has trained many gynaecologists in the field of laparoscopy and hysteroscopy. She specializes in advanced laparoscopic surgeries like hysterectomy for large fibroids, fibroid removal surgeries, Endometriosis, Fertility enhancing surgery, Laparoscopic cancer surgery and surgery for urinary incontinence.
